This is about rewarding players for doing going down an alternative path (i.e. raiding) and getting rewarded for it without cause the huge discrepancies in player power.   Raiders become more powerful raiders without becoming globally uber.   Let skilled grouping players gain benefits via that route, let raiders have a route.    Its about letting the most skilled and dedicated be rewarded without having an Uber Guild tag sticking out of their head.<br />
